    " <leader>gb maps to :Gblame<CR>
    nnoremap <leader>gs :Gstatus<CR>
    " <leader>gd maps to :Gdiff<CR>  和现有冲突
    " <leader>gl maps to :Glog<CR>
    " <leader>gc maps to :Gcommit<CR>
    " <leader>gp maps to :Git push<CR>
